TopicTitle: Any news from the logo contest ?

Articles.Content:
Hi,

after the last announce here which is quite old now, nothing more has been added on this topic, so I wonder where are the winners ? Where are the winning logos ?

There is this thread but it's just pointless guessing.

Could it be possible those logos was so amazing that winners have been abducted and kerbalized ?

winners have been abducted and kerbalized ?

You know to much for your own good. Be warned. Strange forces beyond your comprehension have taken notice.

Also, I too would like to know who the winners are.
Maybe they will add the names to the credits, and also add the flags to the game in 0.24
I think they said at some point that they will be used in 0.24.
They will be in the "contractor logos" in 0.24.
I, too, am interested in this because I *still* have no email from Squad about my winning entries.
